title: Hour 1 - NFL Week 8 Recap, CFP Possibilities
itunes:title: Hour 1 - NFL Week 8 Recap, CFP Possibilities
description:
Dan and the Danettes dissect the games over the weekend and which teams are heading on which trajectories. And they talk about the latest CFP rankings and whether Tennessee has a real shot at a playoff spot.
